Title: Unyielding Fists: Trial of Wood
Description: You have progressed in your training, I think. Come with me, and we will attempt the Trial of Wood.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Master Bruised Paw, then successfully strike the Stack of Wooden Blocks 4 times.
RewardText:
You have the gift of focus, $n. Not many of my students make it this far.

<Master Bruised Paw glances over at Lin.>

Objectives.Text: Strike the Stack of Wooden Boards
